      "review_summary": "The PR changes Slack Socket Mode reconnect policy from a 12-attempt cap to unlimited retries and adds a changelog entry.\n\nPR surface: Source 0, Docs +1. Total +1 across 2 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. Current main still caps Slack Socket Mode reconnects at 12 and throws at exhaustion, and linked redacted logs show the finite retry symptom plus after-patch `retry 1/∞` behavior.",
